{
  "stem": "7722.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She knows-- knows no other-- only father, I am.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I know she's my-- [CRYING] she's my daughter.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There is a name-- what the-- what the-- there is such a Jewish name.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They called her in Jewish, Nuna.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Nuna and-- Nuna is-- we came here, she became Ann, A-N-N, she became.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She came A-N-N.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I married her, and we got a job.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it so happened over there, there was a Ukrainian in this town-- there was over there a Ukrainian, what I used to-- [LAUGHS] I used to give a lot of money, did a lot for me with the railroad cars.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You see, he was the head of the conductors.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I-- I had to-- I had to give him money, because he did a lot.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So later on, when I came to this town, he was from this town.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he had a big house.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he took-- he took me into his house.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he gave me half of the house.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I lived in this-- and I lived in this-- in-- in this house.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, there were.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My older daughter-- she went in the beginning-- she went to a Russian school.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now, she does [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My older daughter is-- she went over there, she did.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] She's very-- she's-- both my-- both my daughters are very bright.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My second daughter was born already.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You see, I was working for the-- for the Russians-- I mean, for the Soviet Union-- till 1946.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then they came-- then they passed a law-- only the Jewish people who were citizens of the-- of Poland had the right to go to Poland, because they were over there anyway.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I decided, it's no-- I don't want to stay in the town.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
